General.Name: Mighty Craft Ltd
General.Description: Mighty Craft Limited engages in the acquisition and operation of various breweries, distilleries, bars, and restaurants in Australia. The company sells its products under the Seven Seasons, Better Beer, Mismatch Brewing Co, 78 Degrees, Hills Cider, Jetty Road Brewery, Ballistic Beer Co, Kangaroo Island Spirits, Torquay Beverage Company, Slipstream, Sparkke, Sauce Brewing Co, Brogan's Way, and Foghorn Brewery brands. The company was formerly known as Founders First Limited and changed its name to Mighty Craft Limited in November 2020. Mighty Craft Limited was incorporated in 2017 and is based in Hawthorn East, Australia.
